      "semantics": {
        "summary": "Shift by a register count, optionally storing the last shifted-out bit in K. With reg_count, count=0 leaves dest unchanged and does not update K; LEFTSHIFT and logical RIGHTSHIFT with count>width yield 0, while arithmetic RIGHTSHIFT with count>=width saturates to the original sign bit."
